### 🚫 What happens if you **don't use keys**?

- React will show a **warning** in the console.
- It may cause performance issues or **incorrect UI updates** when the list changes.

---

### 🟢 Summary:
| Concept | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| 🔑 Key | Unique identifier for each element |
| 📈 Benefit | Optimized re-rendering |
| ❌ Bad Key | Using array index (only safe if list never changes) |
| ✅ Good Key | Use a stable, unique ID like `item.id` |

